bth.advancements.exploration.root.title: Beyond The Horizon
bth.advancements.exploration.tower.title: I can see my house from here!
Slay the Pharaoh and free the Temple from his curse.
bth.advancements.exploration.tiny_coin.d: Start collecting coins for the portal to Ratlantis.
bth.chat.first_start_message: Welcome to Beyond the Horizon! Press 'J' to open the quest book.
bth.chat.no_bounty: You don't have an active bounty in your inventory for capturing this entity.
bountiful.bounty.turnin: Fulfill your bounty by right-clicking on a bounty board.

bountiful.entry.photography_obj_nether_r: Take a selfie in a Nether Reactor in The Nether.

bountiful.entry.photography_obj_sanctum: Take a selfie in a Sanctum in The Nether.

death.attack.coconut_maul.item: %s just got coconut mauled by %s using %s
effect.galosphere.block_bane.description: Deals damage to the target when they place a block.
effect.galosphere.astral.description: Allows the target to phase through blocks.
enchantment.galosphere.rupture.desc: Extends the duration of pink salt pillars.
enchantment.galosphere.sustain.desc: Pink salt pillars shatter into shards when they retract.
item_effect.bth.ancient_cookie_eaten: Your senses sharpen, letting you within seconds see a rift in space that can take you to a faraway place...
item_effect.bth.lembas_bread_0: You feel the essence of the ancients...
item_effect.bth.lembas_bread_1: Crunchy on the outside, but soft on the inside.
item_effect.bth.lembas_bread_3: Ancient magic is coursing through your veins.
item_effect.bth.nanobot_soda_3: Technology and magic is coursing through your veins.
bth.information.bth.bounty_proof: To obtain, use a Spectre Snare on a mob while the associated Bounty is in your inventory.
bth.information.bountiful.bountyboard: Bounty Boards can't be crafted, but can be found in villages.
bth.information.eccentrictome.filled_ecc: Crafting an Eccentric Tome using four bookshelves will provide one filled with the starting manuals. The recipe that uses one bookshelf will be empty.
bth.information.eccentrictome.reverting: Right-click to select a book to read. Left-click in the air to revert the tome back to select a new book.
bth.information.farmersdelight.mushroom_: Grown by planting mushrooms on Rich Soil.
bth.information.rats.charged_creeper_chu: Obtained by killing a Charged Creeper.
bth.information.rats.tiny_coin: These can be found in many structures. The farther you are from spawn, the more abundant they become.
bth.information.supplementaries.urn: Found underground. They will drop when mined with Silk Touch (including whatever loot they hold).
bth.information.tetra.scannable_blocks: Can be detected using a Holosphere upgraded with an Eye of Ender.
bth.information.waystones.waystone: Waystones can't be crafted, but can be found throughout thet world in villages and ancient towers.
filled_map.aether_bronze_dungeon: The Slider hides in the rocks
filled_map.aether_silver_dungeon: The Valkyrie Queen shows no mercy
filled_map.aether_platinum_dungeon: No one escapes the Aerwhale King
filled_map.bth_structures_magician_house: A cozy house in a spooky forest
filled_map.bth_structures_battle_grounds: Once a battle took place here
filled_map.graveyard_ruins: Old ruins with a key to the Corrupted Champion
spell.bth.terminus_singularity.guide:
A black hole like spell that comes with the Terminus blade.

Can not be crafted.
spell.bth.terminus_space_fold.guide:
A teleportation spell that comes with the Terminus blade.

Teleports you through blocks and to entities.

Can not be crafted.
tooltip.bth.aercloud: §7Can be found in similar color biomes.
tooltip.bth.ancient_cookie:
When eaten opens a temporary portal to a random location up to 10,000 blocks away from spawn (configurable). 

Note: might take up to 1-2 minutes to find a suitable location.
tooltip.bth.bounty_proof: Proof that a mob was captured with a Spectre Snare. Hand in together with the bounty.
tooltip.bth.coconut_maul: Share this with all ur friends to totally Coconut Maul them.
tooltip.bth.lembas_bread: A bread baked with ancient magic.
tooltip.bth.mallorn_leaf: Keeps bread fresh for a very long time. Right-click on Elven Gateway Core to recycle for a reward.
tooltip.bth.nanobot_soda_bottle_empty: A bottle designed to hold nanobots.
tooltip.bth.spectre_snare: A tool used by bounty hunters to capture their targets.
tooltip.bth.alexscaves.biome_treat: Punch the ground with it to bind to biome.
